column5: I'm in Gogama fishing out of a rented boat. I've been feeling under the weather so its just worms and jigs and taken 'er easy for me. Here has been my night: Nothing, nothing, nothing followed by nothing ... Then WHAM! Huge 20incher. Hahaha biggest one for me, looks like a simcoe specimen. That was 3 mins ago, sorry no pics. Vertical jigging is now my favorite bass technique
haha good for you! Sometimes its those nothing nothing nothing days that the big one finally shows up to change the worst day ever to the best!
No Pics???? Didn't happen  JK Chad......Congrats
Awesome Mr. Chad Taken 'er easy means, you forgot your tournament sign.... say it ain't so Congrats on your PB

Thanks Rizzo, I've fished this lake twice before and got skunked on all outings... I guess it was all part of the build-up to that pig of a fish!     Hahaha. You'll have to trust me I got one pic of it on my tackled box but I can't upload it now coz I'm using my phone to access OFC. I guess it doesn't count for the tourny without the OFC tourney logo, right?

Ha, yup, taken 'er easy means I forgot the sign in the truck, d'oh. But I used the OFC measuring tape for a crude photo, it has the OFC logo ... Can the OFC tourney jury lend some pity to a guy with a broken stomach? Haha, if not, then oh well.
they don't take kindly to photoshop...i know, i tried.
Ah don't worry about it Chad.... send it in to Geoff anyway and see what he says.... you never know

My puppy also ran away today.  Hahaha that's that then! I should make t-shirts for team 8 with the tourny logo printed on the front... ONLY team 8, the ASSASSASSIN8ORS!!! Wow, that sounds terrible with the extra a...
